'''''History of the Galaxy, Parts One, Two and Three''''' was a<ref name="Far Far Away" /> popular<ref name="Insider">{{InsiderCite|225|A Certain Point of View}}</ref> three-part story that [[Mark IV architect droid|Mark IV]] [[architect droid]] [[Huyang]] told to the [[Jedi Initiate|Jedi younglings]] at the [[Imperial Palace|Jedi Temple]]. The former [[Jedi]] [[Ahsoka Tano]] considered the first part to be the best. During their journey to [[Far galaxy|another galaxy]] along the [[Pathway to Peridea]], Huyang and Tano discussed the story.<ref name="Far Far Away" />

